social_posts.post_text:
I'm grateful for not anything but everything
Every loss I had to take. I took it on the chin. One day we will win again
Front line when it’s war time
32 years around the sun!!! Thank you for allowing me to see another year… more life more blessings
32nd starting off the right way🔑Proud to announce that I will be opening a @lvlxbeautybar Fayetteville coming soon! S/o to @bre.nicole for letting me franchise!

What a day this was… was blessed to see where Jesus was crucified, where he was laid to rest.. seen where  the last supper was held… I’m so blessed and fortunate to have been able to see this a experience I’ll never forget… my love for Israel is everlasting ❤️❤️❤️

Hapoel Tel Aviv where do I began…  The amount of love here is unmatched it’s truly unbelievable… being able to play in front of you guys was truly a honor… I’ve been lucky to have some great teammates through my career but this year was incredible.. the guys felt like family and made me feel like I was apart of their family.. I can leave here with no regrets or sadness, I gained brothers, and Israel has become a second home for me.. I just want to say I’m forever grateful for this year.. I have  lifelong memories… sometime as athletes we think people are blessed to have us but I was blessed that you guys took me in with open arms and love… I love you guys so much I hope we meet again…. ❤️🤍❤️🤍❤️🤍
